{
  "id": "63b4379042a47f001e45480c",
  "title": "謙遜について",
  "created": 1672755089,
  "updated": 1672755089,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "63b4379042a47f001e45480c",
      "text": "謙遜について",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06eb",
      "text": "from [インポスターシンドローム]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06ec",
      "text": "謙遜について",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06ed",
      "text": "[謙遜]について[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06ee",
      "text": "　「すごいですね」的なことを言われたときに反射的に「いやいや、そんなことないですよ」と言ってしまうことがある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06ef",
      "text": " これを「謙遜」と呼んでポジティブに捉える文化がある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f0",
      "text": " 一方で、これは相手の「すごいと思った」感情をバッサリ切り捨てちゃう行為でもある",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f1",
      "text": " 的な話を人生のどこかのタイミングで見かけて「確かにそうだなー」と思ったので「いやいや、そんなことないです」と言いたくなった時に「ありがとうございます」と返すようにしている",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f2",
      "text": "  +1[/villagepump/inajob.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f3",
      "text": "   娘を誉められた時も同じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f4",
      "text": "  返すようにはしてるけど納得はできてない[/villagepump/yosider.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f5",
      "text": "  　別に納得はしなくてもいいんだろうなあ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f6",
      "text": "  　そう言われたという事実をそのまま受け取る",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f7",
      "text": "  　「納得」はしてないし、する必要もないと思う[/villagepump/nishio.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f8",
      "text": "  　 「へー、あなたはそう思うんですね」みたいな感じ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06f9",
      "text": "  　 ポジティブな評価でもネガティブな評価でも「あなたはそう思うのですね」にすぎない",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06fa",
      "text": "  　 「受け止める」と「納得する」は別物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06fb",
      "text": "  　 　ここで書いたな",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06fc",
      "text": "  　　 　[KJ法勉強会@ロフトワーク 講義資料v1#62cfeec6aff09e0000a89677]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06fd",
      "text": "  　 　人の主張Aを受け止めることと、その主張の内容が真であると信じることは別物",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06fe",
      "text": "  　 　「この人はAと言った」は観測事実",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc06ff",
      "text": "  　 　　Aは解釈",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc0700",
      "text": "  　 　　事実と解釈は別",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
    {
      "id": "63b43790aff09e0000bc0701",
      "text": " 「[他者の評価を受け止める]」の具体例",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1672755089,
      "updated": 1672755089
    },
